1.0.0.name: connect20/Enquiry
1.0.0.description: Enquiry Management Magento Feedback Extension enables your customer to ask questions(any doubts) and submit inquiry regarding any product.Enquiry link in the header takes customers straight to the Magento feedback & enquiry form. All queries are managed from the backend interface which allows you to track and reply any one instantly.

suggest.magento-hackathon\/magento-composer-inst: Allows to manage this package as a dependency
